"title": "5480: protection",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5480",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Defence from attack, hurt or exploitation. The ultimate protector is God but he also uses others in defending the weak and needy.</p>\n<h2>Protection from oppression</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:4\">PSA 72:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:18\">DEU 10:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps12:5\">PSA 12:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:10\">PSA 35:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:51-Luke1:53\">LUK 1:51–1:53</a></p>\n<h2>Protection from exploitation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:3-Job24:4\">JOB 24:3–24:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:14\">PRO 30:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:10-Ezek18:13\">EZK 18:10–18:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos4:1\">AMO 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:4-Amos8:6\">AMO 8:4–8:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:38-Mark12:40\">MRK 12:38–12:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:1-Jas5:6\">JAS 5:1–5:6</a></p>\n<h2>Means of protection against physical attack</h2>\n<h3>Armour</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:38\">1SA 17:38</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:11\">1KI 20:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:4\">JER 46:4</a></p>\n<h3>Shields</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:3\">JER 46:3</a></p>\n<h3>Helmets</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:38\">1SA 17:38</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:4\">JER 46:4</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritual protection</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:11-John17:12\">JHN 17:11–17:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:28-John10:29\">JHN 10:28–10:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:13\">1CO 10:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:6\">PHP 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:7\">PHP 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:12\">2TI 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:5\">1PE 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:24\">JUD 1:24</a></p>\n<h2>Believers need protection from spiritual dangers</h2>\n<h3>From Satan</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:8\">1PE 5:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:9\">JOB 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:13\">MAT 6:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:15\">JHN 17:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:11-Eph6:12\">EPH 6:11–6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:9\">2TH 2:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:3\">2TH 3:3</a></p>\n<h3>From Satan's agents in the world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:18-John15:19\">JHN 15:18–15:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:2\">PSA 27:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:15\">PSA 31:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps109:1-Ps109:3\">PSA 109:1–109:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps109:31\">PSA 109:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:2-Mic7:3\">MIC 7:2–7:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:28-Matt10:29\">MAT 10:28–10:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:36\">MAT 10:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:68-Luke1:74\">LUK 1:68–1:74</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:36\">ROM 8:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:13\">1JN 3:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:4\">1JN 4:4</a></p>\n<h2>God protects his people</h2>\n<h3>By watching over them and helping them</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps121:5\">PSA 121:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:9\">1SA 2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:6\">PSA 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:15\">PSA 34:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:40\">PSA 37:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:17\">PSA 40:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:1\">PSA 140:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:10\">2CO 1:10</a></p>\n<h3>By his presence with them</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:5\">HEB 13:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:5\">JOS 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:116\">PSA 119:116</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:170\">PSA 119:170</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:1-Isa43:3\">ISA 43:1–43:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:33\">JHN 16:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:10\">ACT 18:10</a></p>\n<h3>By sending angels to protect them</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:7\">PSA 34:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:17\">GEN 21:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:20\">EXO 23:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:22\">NUM 22:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:24\">NUM 22:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:26\">NUM 22:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:31\">NUM 22:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:34\">NUM 22:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:17\">2KI 6:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:11\">PSA 91:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:10\">MAT 18:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:14\">HEB 1:14</a></p>\n<h3>By using people to defend them</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:8-Prov31:9\">PRO 31:8–31:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num35:25\">NUM 35:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:17\">ISA 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:6\">ISA 58:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:28\">JER 5:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:16\">JER 22:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:33-Luke10:35\">LUK 10:33–10:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:27\">JAS 1:27</a></p>\n<h2>Conditions of God's protection</h2>\n<h3>Prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:12\">PSA 72:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:23\">JOB 6:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:1\">PSA 59:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps82:3\">PSA 82:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:19\">PSA 145:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:11\">JHN 17:11</a></p>\n<h3>Right attitudes</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:14\">PSA 91:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut23:14\">DEU 23:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:6\">PSA 116:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:7-Prov2:8\">PRO 2:7–2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:11\">PRO 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:6\">PRO 11:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:3\">PRO 14:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:7\">1CO 13:7</a></p>",
